N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 8 ยง 339.1 - Requirement

State Regulations

Members of the professional staff, other than persons
having temporary appointments, shall, if eligible, become members of either the

New York State Employees Retirement System or the New York State Teachers

Retirement System, or shall elect the optional retirement
program. Notes
